Objective:
Integrate the OPS UI Octobot BFF service with the MFE application and validate the end-to-end communication between UI and backend services.

Scope of Work:

Connect OPS UI Octobot BFF APIs with the MFE application.
Configure required API endpoints, request/response mappings, and environment settings.
Validate authentication, routing, and connectivity between MFE and BFF.
Perform integration testing for the expected user flows.
Identify and fix any integration issues found during testing.

Expected Outcome:
OPS UI Octobot BFF should be successfully integrated with the MFE application and validated on the required environment.

Acceptance Criteria:

MFE is able to call the required BFF APIs successfully.
API responses are displayed/handled correctly in the UI.
No major integration or connectivity errors are observed.
Integration testing is completed and results are updated in the task
